1) Initialize package.json
in root folder : npm init -y

2) update the command in "scripts/test" 
    node app/index.js

3) install node modules
npm install express
npm install hbs

4) from a terminal, run
npm run test

5) Deployment (Heroku)
heroku login
git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit"
heroku create <app_name>
git push heroku master


